  "description": "A nighttime panoramic view of a city skyline with bridges prominently featured. The foreground shows a modern cable-stayed bridge illuminated with white and red lights, extending across dark water. Behind it, a classic suspension bridge is visible, also lit up, adding a layered depth to the scene. The cityscape is densely packed with illuminated buildings, including a towering skyscraper with a bright blue peak. Fireworks are exploding in the sky above the buildings, creating a burst of vibrant color against the dark backdrop. The overall impression is one of a lively and vibrant urban landscape.",
